"{\"uid\": \"fox32chicago.com-news-bears-star-cole-kmet-teams-up-united-airlines-support-special-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Share  Bears' Cole Kmet is giving back to the Special Olympics community after surprising United Airlines customers at O'Hare International Airport.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Kmet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cole Kmet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Kmet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Kmet\"}, {\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2737675817007051e-12, \"text\": \"United Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CHICAGO-AChicago Bearsstar partnered with United Airlines to show support for Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2737675817007051e-12, \"text\": \"United Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8735177046142883e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tight end Cole Kmet worked alongside the airline's Special Olympics Service Ambassadors all day Wednesday and helped spread the word about a program that gives the athletes a chance to work for United.\", \"from\": 247, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8735177046142883e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kmet met two of United Airlines' Special Olympics service ambassadors as they helped passengers board a flight to Texas.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2737675817007051e-12, \"text\": \"United Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8735177046142883e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9952233045604489, \"rank\": 0.003395906460677719, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been working with them now for about a year.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a great organization - something I am really fond to be a part of.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have done things like the Polar Plunge back in March.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just a great organization and anything I can do to help uplift the athletes, I want to be a part of,\\\" said Kmet.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KTWV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.415569035737841e-18, \"text\": \"Kmet\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KTWV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KTWV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ambassadors program started five years ago.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"United hires four Special Olympics athletes to work at O'Hare International Airport - 18 nationwide - to greet passengers and help them navigate their way through Terminal One.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8735177046142883e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a busy airport, so helping passengers know where their gate is, helping them know where security is\\u2026 I enjoy showing kindness and love to all of the passengers that are flying on United,\\\" said Daniel Smrokowsi, a service ambassador.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kmet's visit also called attention to United's Miles on a Mission Program, in which loyalty members can donate their unused air miles to the Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KTWV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.415569035737841e-18, \"text\": \"Kmet\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KTWV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KTWV\"}, {\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8735177046142883e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This allows athletes to fly to events all over the world for free.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Really, the goal of the program is to deepen our relationship with Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8735177046142883e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We realized some of the athletes are incredibly talents and could bring a really unique skill set to United Airlines,\\\" said Kristin Lewis, with the airline.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1753, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2737675817007051e-12, \"text\": \"United Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristin_Halvorsen\", \"score\": 0.9632585623876607, \"rank\": 0.021326439925371875, \"text\": \"Kristin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristin_Halvorsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristin_Halvorsen\"}, {\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Lewis\", \"score\": 0.9375441834181174, \"rank\": 0.06659014838544212, \"text\": \"Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Lewis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Special Olympics athletes we spoke with said the public has made them better athletes because it's giving them the confidence they need to succeed.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the morning news in under five minutes.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By clicking Sign Up, I confirmthat I have read and agreeto thePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Service.\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, or redistributed.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025 FOX Television Stations\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2188, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Television_Stations\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FOX Television Stations\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Television_Stations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Television_Stations\"}]}]}"